h3(#ContextHelpButton_constr). ContextHelpButton.new

h4. Parameters

* _parent_ Parent window. Must not be NULL.
* _id_ Button identifier. Defaults to ID_CONTEXT_HELP.
* _pos_ Button position.
* _size_ Button size. If the default size (-1, -1) is specified then the button is sized
appropriately for the question mark bitmap.
* _style_ Window style.

h4. Remarks

Normally you need pass only the parent window to the constructor, and use the defaults for the remaining parameters.

